00:28:02.986 --> 00:28:04.995
Coba kulihat.

420
00:28:04.995 --> 00:28:06.825
"Aku cinta kau." "Kau lagi apa?"

421
00:28:06.825 --> 00:28:08.166
"Aku besok libur."

422
00:28:08.166 --> 00:28:10.166
